{"type":"miscellaneous","title":"Turtle Shell","summaries":["The <b>Turtle Shell</b> is a <linked>Hardmode</linked> <linked>crafting material</linked> that has a <span class=\"eico i1 i2 i4\" title=\"Desktop, Console and Mobile versions\"><b></b><i></i></span> <span class=\"chance\"><s>8.33*</s>1/12 (8.33%)</span> / <span class=\"eico i3 i5 i6\" title=\"Old-gen console, 3DS and Legacy tModLoader versions\"><b></b><i></i></span> <span class=\"chance\"><s>5.88*</s>1/17 (5.88%)</span> chance of being dropped by the <linked>Giant Tortoises</linked> in the Hardmode <linked>Jungle</linked> and <linked>Underground Jungle</linked>.","Turtle Shells are used solely to craft <linked>Turtle armor</linked>, which can in turn be used to craft <linked>Beetle armor</linked>. Crafting all pieces of Turtle armor requires a total of 3 Turtle Shells, but, since Beetle Armor has two chest variants, you would need 4 Turtle Shells to craft the armor with both chest pieces. On average, you will need to kill about 90 Giant Tortoises for a 90% chance to get 3 Turtle Shells (about 140 for 99%). If you want to get 4 Turtle Shells instead, this number is raised to 110 for 90% chance (and 170 for 99%)."],"statistics":{"Rarity":"<span class=\"rarity\"><linked>[img:Rarity level: 7]</linked></span>","Sell":"<span class=\"coin\" title=\"10 Silver Coins\" data-sort-value=\"1000\"><span class=\"sc\">10</span></span>","Research":"<abbr class=\"journey\" title=\"Journey Mode\">3 required</abbr>"},"crafts":{"Used in":[{"result":{"rowspan":1,"value":"<span class=\"i multi-line\"><linked>[img:Turtle Helmet]</linked><span><span><linked>Turtle Helmet</linked></span></span></span>"},"ingredients":{"value":"<ul><li><span class=\"i\"><linked>[img:Chlorophyte Bar]</linked><span><span><linked>Chlorophyte Bar</linked></span></span></span> <span class=\"note-text\">(12)</span></li><li><span class=\"i\"><linked>[img:Turtle Shell]</linked><span><span><linked>Turtle Shell</linked></span></span></span></li></ul>"},"sta